title: Dajubilus Latin Ensemble Discography 2011-2013 (2 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
DAJUBILUS LATIN ENSEMBLE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 2 releases...

 * 2011 - Dancing In The Spirit
 * 2013 - No Hay Nada Mejor

An exquisite blend of Bossa Nova, Samba, R&B, New Age and Latin rythms with a touch of Jazz.  DaJubilus Latin Ensemble combines rythms of Caribbean, R&B, Latin Bossa/Samba that will sooth your heart and soul.

Blessings,
TorrentTracts - October 2013
